verbose_text: Additionally, rs6695435, an intergenic variant located 4 kb upstream of the TSS of TBX19 (MIM 604614), had a subtle but not significant association with mRNA expression as measured by RNA-seq (p = 0.28, beta = 0.14) (XREF_FIG C), but a significant association with concordant effect direction on TBX19 protein levels (p = 5.17 x 10 -6, beta = 0.33) and was one of the closest cis pQTLs to the TSS of the gene model that we identified.
